step.patterns:
- Use {{site.data.keyword.powerSys_notm}} variable
- Include deployment tags: [{{site.data.keyword.off-prem}}]{: tag-blue}
- Use heading level ## for questions
- Add anchors: {: #anchor-name}
- Include {: faq} tag

step.format:
## [Question text]
{: #section-anchor-name}
{: faq}

[Deployment tags if applicable]

Answer text with proper formatting and links.
